oved being a woman, I''ve loved being a mother, I''ve loved being a grandmother. I want three words: Woman, Atheist, Anarchist. That''s me.', 10467, 0), (267122, 'What is nobler," she mused, turning over the photographs, "than to be a woman to whom every one turns, in sorrow or difficulty?', 113, 0), (267123, 'Have you noticed her name?"Kit leaned sideways to see the letters painted jauntily on the transom. "The WITCH! How did you dare? Does Hannah know?" "Oh, she''s not named after Hannah. I hadn''t gone ten miles down the river that day before I knew I''d left the real witch behind.', 7333, 0), (267124, 'He caught his breath, not because of her bedraggled appearance, but rather because of the way she stood, so straight and tall. Courageous.', 18686, 0), (267125, 'Remember! When you tell a woman that she cooks something very good', 45925, 0), (267126, 'Every woman’s heart cannot be opened with words', 45926, 0), (267127, 'A woman never argues with a compliment.', 45927, 0), (267128, 'Though a modern woman’s computer is more intimate than her bed...', 44574, 0), (267129, 'When I look in the mirror, I see a woman with secrets. When we don’t listen to our intuition, we abandon our souls. And we abandon our souls because we are afraid if we don’t, others will abandon us.', 9108, 0), (267130, 'The one thing you should never do to a woman, whether you make love to her or fuck her, is apologise straight after.', 6452, 0), (267131, 'However impatient she might be in the day, however filled with little sudden angers, at night she was all tenderness.', 442, 0), (267132, 'Why do you think there aren’t rules to how sex will work? You didn’t want to talk to me about what you wanted. You pushed me into the room so I wouldn’t turn on the light because you knew damn well I would push back on that, didn’t you?”She stayed where she was. “Yes. I don’t want you to see me. I don’t look like one of those girls in a magazine.”He groaned, the sound coming from deep in his chest. “Those gi